snippet.title: JellyCar version 1.1 - Rocket Launch
snippet.description:
one of the new levels in JellyCar v1.1 "Rocket Launch".

sounds are all sped up because the video was captured at 30fps, and then sped up to 60fps to represent actual gameplay :)

more on the game at walaber.com
